textOne.text: Hello, I'm Shiroko - Newbie Developer. I've only been learning coding for 4 weeks and this is my first product. So it still has a lot of error, so please feel free to comment.

textTwo.text: I use discord and messenger every day to communicate and work so you can always interact with me through them. And I hope we can become good friends through this product.

textThree.text: My life is full of challenges, but fortunately for me, I found her - she always comes to me when I'm happy and tries to encourage me every day to overcome the difficulties of life. That's why I love her so much.
